title.rendered: STEDI Short Type RJ45 UHF Pass Through To Suit Toyota

content.rendered:
Toyota RJ45 Connector

OVERVIEW

Coming Soon.

ILLUMINATION

Coming Soon.

APPLICATION

Coming Soon.

DETAILS

RJ45 pass-through connector

This RJ45 pass-through connector allows for a UHF fitted with an RJ45 connector to be plugged in.

COMPATIBLE TOYOTA MAKES

Toyota RAV4 | 2006 to 2011
Toyota Landcruiser 200 Series | 2008 to Current (2017+)
Toyota Prado 200 Series | 2015 – Onward
Toyota Prado 150 Series | 2010 – Onward
Toyota Hilux 2015 – Onwards (Current model)
Toyota Fortuner 2016 – Onwards
Toyota Camry 2011 – 2014
Toyota Corolla 2006 – 2013
Toyota Tacoma 2012 – 2014 (Center console)
Toyota Tundra 2007 – 2014
Toyota Kluger 2008 – current

The faceplate locks into place within the existing switch blank. The RJ45 pass-through connector is fully replaceable (not glued in).

SPECIFICATIONS

BACK LIGHT COLOUR Blue
SURFACE SIZE DIMENSIONS 32.5mmx22mm

 

WHAT’S IN THE BOX

  • 1 x Toyota RJ45 Connector UHF
